.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.production.example

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Docker (avoid recursive context)
docker-compose*.yml

# Documentation
*.md
!README.md
LICENSE

# Tests (not needed in production images)
tests/
